**Climate Gamification** is a fully interactive web application that visualizes survey results about climate change in a **gamified 3D environment**.  

After completing a short climate survey, users receive **personalized feedback** represented through animated, color-coded cards and can explore **other participantsâ€™ results** in a live, orbitable 3D world.

